    "description": "<p><strong>Company overview</strong></p>\n<p>Urban Facility Services has been around since 2000. Re-established in 2021 as a Pte Ltd company we have now embarked on building a stronghold in the building services industry.</p>\n<p>Incorporating automation and systems, we are able to provide quality services while focusing on human resources as the backbone of our business. By striving to become an exemplary employer our efforts are reaped through quality work.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>MISSION</strong></p>\n<p>Our mission is to provide an edge to the industry and all its stakeholders.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>VISION</strong></p>\n<p>The chosen service provider of total property services. A firm that leads by example on corporate and social responsibilities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are expanding aggressively and are looking for passionate and high potential individuals to join our family.</p>",
